<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Smack3" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Smack,</orth> vb. to have a taste or tincture: <cit><quote>my father did something s., he had a kind of taste,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.2.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 2, 18</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>whether I s. or no,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 1.209" default="NO" valid="yes">John I, 209</bibl></cit>. With <emph>of</emph>: <cit><quote>all sects, all ages s. of this vice,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 2.2.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 2, 5</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>nothing she does or seems but --s of something greater than herself,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.158" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 158</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. jn 1.208" default="NO" valid="yes">John I, 208</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 2.396.158" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 396</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.2.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 2, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.59" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 59</bibl>.

<pb n="1075" />
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>